page.title: 20CREDITS.
page.content:
This Domesday Project Disc,has been put together by all of the First Year at Swakeleys Girls School in Hillingdon. This disc mentions many different things that are in Hillingdon. The First Year forms that did this were:
1 Collins = Miss Collins 1 Atkinson = Mr Klymow 1 Thompson = Mr Barker 1 Healy = Mr Barker 1 Wheeler = Mr Bremner
The people that were responsible for putting the information on the disc were: Mr Barker, Louise Collett, Alison Powell, Helen Tungate, Kerry Atkins, Sukbinder Bassi and Susan Terry. Mr Bremner took the photographs.
